<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q27_v12" title="Q27_v12" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Registro del caso:</p>
    <p>
      En una bodega escolar se venden cajas de lápices. En la etiqueta de una de las cajas se muestra el siguiente registro de contenido: "Contenido: 2 cajas contienen 36 lápices".
      Si un colegio compra c cajas de este tipo, ¿cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa el número total de lápices 
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo>
      </m:math>
      ?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>c</m:mi>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">
          ¡Correcto! Si 2 cajas contienen 36 lápices, entonces 1 caja contiene 18 lápices. Por lo tanto, c cajas contienen 
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>c</m:mi>
          </m:math>
          lápices, así que la expresión correcta es 
          <m:math>
            <m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>c</m:mi>
          </m:math>.
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mn>18</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
          <m:mi>c</m:mi>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">
          Incorrecto. Del dato 2 cajas = 36 lápices se obtiene que 1 caja = 18 lápices. Entonces, para c cajas el total debe aumentar multiplicando por 18, no por 
          <m:math>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>1</m:mn>
              <m:mn>18</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
          </m:math>.
          Por ejemplo, si 
          <m:math>
            <m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:math>,
          esta opción da
          <m:math>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>1</m:mn>
              <m:mn>18</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn>
              <m:mn>18</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
          </m:math>
          lápices, pero el enunciado indica 36 lápices.
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">
          Incorrecto. El número total de lápices debe ser proporcional a la cantidad de cajas. Como 1 caja contiene 18 lápices, c cajas contienen 
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>c</m:mi>
          </m:math>
          lápices. Por ejemplo, si 
          <m:math>
            <m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:math>,
          esta opción da 
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn>
          </m:math>,
          pero el enunciado indica que 2 cajas contienen 36 lápices.
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">
          Incorrecto. Si 2 cajas contienen 36 lápices, entonces cada caja contiene 18 lápices y el total para c cajas es 
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>c</m:mi>
          </m:math>.
          Esta opción no representa ese total. Por ejemplo, si 
          <m:math>
            <m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:math>,
          esta opción da 
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>-16</m:mn>
          </m:math>,
          pero el enunciado indica 36 lápices.
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="FB_NoResponse" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p>Debes seleccionar una alternativa para recibir retroalimentación específica.</p>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Interpretar el dato de la etiqueta</strong></p>
            <p>La etiqueta dice que 2 cajas contienen 36 lápices.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular cuántos lápices tiene 1 caja</strong></p>
            <p>Si 2 cajas contienen 36 lápices, entonces 1 caja contiene la mitad:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>36</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>18</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces, cada caja contiene 18 lápices.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Expresar el total para c cajas</strong></p>
            <p>Si una caja tiene 18 lápices, entonces c cajas tienen:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>c</m:mi>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la función es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>c</m:mi>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar con el dato original</strong></p>
            <p>Si 
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:math>,
              entonces:
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Coincide exactamente con la información de la etiqueta.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión correcta es la alternativa A:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>c</m:mi>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_NoResponse</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>